videos.headline: Gundy: 'I'm really proud of our team'
videos.description: Oklahoma State coach Mike Gundy reacts to the Cowboys' win over TCU and talks about how his team has dealt with the homecoming parade accident. Gundy looks ahead to his team's upcoming matchups.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Mike Gundy After Oklahoma State's Win) 2015/11/7 SportsCenter
